Papalabo nila ang iyong paghatol.

00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:30.970
Isipin ang iyong pahinga at pagkain,

00:12:30.970 --> 00:12:32.020
para manatiling maayos ang iyong kalusugan.

00:12:32.020 --> 00:12:32.860
oh

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:34.790
bakit mo ako pinapaalala ng ganito,

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:36.390
parang paalam?

00:12:37.940 --> 00:12:39.360
Ako ay isang karaniwang tao.

00:12:39.870 --> 00:12:41.510
Kapag umakyat ka sa trono ng imperyal,

00:12:41.740 --> 00:12:43.320
malaki ang pagkakaiba natin.

00:12:43.950 --> 00:12:44.800
Noon,

00:12:44.810 --> 00:12:45.960
Baka hindi mo pakinggan ang aking mga salita,

00:12:46.550 --> 00:12:48.260
at hindi rin ako maaaring manatili palagi sa iyong tabi.

00:12:49.510 --> 00:12:50.350
Simple lang yan.

00:12:50.910 --> 00:12:52.270
Sa sandaling umakyat ako sa trono,

00:12:52.660 --> 00:12:53.600
Bibigyan kita ng post.

00:12:53.930 --> 00:12:54.770
Pumili ka.

00:12:56.920 --> 00:12:58.670
Hindi kaya ng babaeng tulad ko

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:00.200
maglingkod bilang isang opisyal.

00:13:01.550 --> 00:13:02.720
Bakit hindi?

00:13:03.750 --> 00:13:07.270
Sobrang pakialam mo sa araw-araw kong buhay.

00:13:08.670 --> 00:13:09.790
Bakit hindi

00:13:10.270 --> 00:13:11.320
gawin kang Empress?

00:13:11.720 --> 00:13:13.480
Pagkatapos ay maaari mo akong bantayan araw-araw

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:14.320
at alagaan mo ako.

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:16.940
talaga?

00:13:17.030 --> 00:13:17.870
talaga.

00:13:18.720 --> 00:13:21.600
Ikaw ang pinakamamahal kong kaibigan
mula pagkabata.

00:13:22.830 --> 00:13:23.960
Sama-sama tayong nagbabahagi ng mga pagpapala,

00:13:24.280 --> 00:13:25.120
kaya bakit hindi?

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:26.960
Buddy?

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:32.150
Sabi ni Heng ng mga malalapit na kaibigan

00:13:32.360 --> 00:13:33.330
dapat tawaging "buddy".

00:13:36.650 --> 00:13:38.240
Babae, gabi na.

00:13:39.390 --> 00:13:40.230
Oh...

00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:42.040
Lumabas ka na ba?

00:13:42.950 --> 00:13:43.790
Babalik ka ba?

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:46.860
Matagal na akong hindi nakabalik.
Balak ng tatay ko

00:13:46.860 --> 00:13:48.120
dalhin mo ako sa pagbisita sa ilang mga kamag-anak.

00:13:49.630 --> 00:13:50.920
Aalis na ako ngayon.

00:13:51.510 --> 00:13:52.350
Mm.

00:14:01.470 --> 00:14:02.390
Duke.

00:14:03.360 --> 00:14:04.630
Isipin ang iyong mga pagkain at magpahinga.

00:14:05.120 --> 00:14:06.120
Manatili sa mabuting kalusugan.

00:14:06.550 --> 00:14:07.390
At gayundin...

00:14:07.650 --> 00:14:09.550
Oh, ngayon mo lang sinabi.

00:14:09.760 --> 00:14:10.850
Naalala ko na lahat.

00:14:11.100 --> 00:14:12.790
Sige na, bumalik ka ng maaga.

00:14:27.070 --> 00:14:28.000
Hihintayin kita.

00:14:45.880 --> 00:14:46.770
aking ginang.

00:14:46.790 --> 00:14:48.440
May naghihintay na karwahe sa labas ng lungsod.

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:49.580
Gabi na.

00:14:49.590 --> 00:14:50.550
Dapat na tayong umalis ngayon.

00:14:50.550 --> 00:14:51.390
Tara na.

00:15:09.750 --> 00:15:10.590
At gayundin...

00:15:11.960 --> 00:15:13.480
Duke, huwag mo akong kalimutan.

00:15:24.480 --> 00:15:25.320
Binebenta ang steamed bun.

00:15:25.960 --> 00:15:27.550
steamed bun na puno ng karne.

00:15:28.080 --> 00:15:30.790
sariwang karne-puno ng steamed bun.

00:15:32.200 --> 00:15:33.750
Sir, gusto mong subukan ang isa?

00:15:35.030 --> 00:15:36.870
Sir, tingnan mo dito.

00:15:36.870 --> 00:15:38.180
Sariwa mula sa bapor.

00:15:38.720 --> 00:15:40.470
Ayokong iwan sina Ama at Ina.

00:15:40.490 --> 00:15:42.340
Nagpasya na ba sila na iwan ako?

00:15:42.340 --> 00:15:44.320
Kaya kong maging mabuti at masunurin.

00:15:44.330 --> 00:15:46.360
Hangga't kaya nilang manatili sa tabi ko.

00:15:46.360 --> 00:15:48.440
Ayaw na nila sa akin.

00:15:48.440 --> 00:15:49.560
Hindi iyon totoo, binibini.

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:51.360
Babalik kami ulit.

00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:53.510
- Maging mabuti.
-Ayoko...

00:15:53.800 --> 00:15:54.670
ayoko.

00:15:54.670 --> 00:15:55.560
Maging mabuti, aking ginang.

00:15:55.580 --> 00:15:56.940
Babalik kami ulit.

00:16:07.320 --> 00:16:08.320
Sandali lang binibini.

00:16:08.480 --> 00:16:09.320
Ito ay isang inspeksyon.

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:11.840
Susunod.

00:16:14.240 --> 00:16:16.020
Ang Imperial Palace ay may sariling mga patakaran.

00:16:16.810 --> 00:16:19.010
Kapag nasa loob ka na, mas mabuting sundin mo sila.

00:16:19.020 --> 00:16:19.860
Tapos na, binibini.

00:16:20.420 --> 00:16:21.360
Makakaalis na tayo.

00:16:21.670 --> 00:16:22.510
aking ginang.

00:16:23.410 --> 00:16:25.270
Aking ginang? Tumakas na siya.

00:16:25.280 --> 00:16:26.600
Wala na siya. Dali, hanapin mo siya.

00:16:26.600 --> 00:16:27.440
aking ginang.

00:16:31.210 --> 00:16:32.980
Hoy, saan ka pupunta?

00:16:34.780 --> 00:16:35.980
Aalis na kami.

00:16:35.990 --> 00:16:37.510
- Saan ka pupunta?
- ako...

00:16:37.510 --> 00:16:38.350
Sumakay ka sa karwahe.

00:16:39.700 --> 00:16:40.710
Huwag mo akong guluhin.

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:41.740
Bilisan mo at sumakay.

00:16:43.190 --> 00:16:44.310
Sige, lahat sa loob.

00:16:49.870 --> 00:16:50.840
Halika, kumilos ka dali.

00:16:51.010 --> 00:16:51.850
Manatili sa likod.

00:16:57.440 --> 00:16:58.280
Bilisan mo, bilisan mo.

00:17:14.440 --> 00:17:15.400
Nakapila lahat.

00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:17.270
Makinig kayong mabuti, lahat.

00:17:17.770 --> 00:17:19.830
Kapag nakilala mo si Empress Dowager, maging matalino.

00:17:20.150 --> 00:17:21.810
Kung pinukaw mo ang kanyang sama ng loob,

00:17:22.800 --> 00:17:25.150
baka masiraan ka lang ng ulo.

00:17:25.440 --> 00:17:26.400
Empress Dowager?

00:17:43.700 --> 00:17:46.100
♪Bantayan ang bagyo;
marinig ang pagbuhos ng ulan sa gabi♪

00:17:46.100 --> 00:17:47.700
♪Hanggang sa liwanag ng bukang-liwayway♪

00:17:47.700 --> 00:17:49.420
♪Isang katotohanang hindi masabi♪

00:17:50.100 --> 00:17:51.780
♪Tama at maling bagay♪

00:17:51.780 --> 00:17:53.900
♪Gayunpaman hindi ako makakagawa ng tamang pagpipilian♪

00:17:54.100 --> 00:17:55.540
♪Ang nawalang manlalaro sa laro♪

00:17:55.780 --> 00:17:58.900
♪Gumawa ng isang liko ng kapalaran♪

00:17:58.900 --> 00:18:01.420
♪Nawala ang daan pabalik,
wala nang babalikan♪

00:18:01.420 --> 00:18:04.660
♪Hiram ang walang katapusang cycle♪

00:18:05.220 --> 00:18:08.700
♪Para ipaglaban ang pinakaperpektong resulta♪

00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:11.820
♪Paano i-trace ang mga thread
at sundin ang sanhi at epekto♪

00:18:11.820 --> 00:18:15.580
♪Naghahanap ng diskarte na walang kapintasan♪

00:18:15.860 --> 00:18:20.500
♪Paano makawala
mula sa nakatadhana ngunit hindi inaasahang lock na ito♪

00:18:20.660 --> 00:18:25.700
♪Upang mabuhay upang niyanig ang mundo♪

00:18:26.060 --> 00:18:30.180
♪Sa paglalakbay na ito,
nagkakaroon ako ng mas matinding kalamangan♪

00:18:30.300 --> 00:18:32.380
♪Nagplano ako
bago ako kumilos nang hindi mabilang na beses♪

00:18:32.460 --> 00:18:38.820
♪Ang nakamamatay na panganib ay naging biro♪

00:18:38.940 --> 00:18:43.140
♪Sa daan na ito,
pinagmamasdan ko ang walang katapusang pagtaas-baba♪

00:18:43.180 --> 00:18:45.260
♪Nasa mga kabanata ang mga edad
ng pagkabulok at pamumulaklak♪

00:18:45.260 --> 00:18:47.180
♪Magkita tayong muli♪

00:18:47.220 --> 00:18:52.380
♪Isang nagmamadaling landas, at ang isa ay maluwag♪

